properties.headline: Tornado Watch issued January 10 at 5:35PM CST until January 11 at 2:00AM CST by NWS Springfield MO
properties.description:
THE NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE HAS ISSUED TORNADO WATCH 5 IN EFFECT
UNTIL 2 AM CST SATURDAY FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS

IN MISSOURI THIS WATCH INCLUDES 13 COUNTIES

IN SOUTH CENTRAL MISSOURI

DENT                  HOWELL                OREGON
SHANNON               TEXAS

IN SOUTHWEST MISSOURI

CHRISTIAN             DOUGLAS               GREENE
OZARK                 STONE                 TANEY
WEBSTER               WRIGHT

THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF ALTON, AVA, BANGERT, BENDAVIS,
BIRCH TREE, BRANSON, CHRISTIAN CENTER, COUCH, CRANE, DARIEN,
DAWSON, DOGWOOD, DUNCAN, EDGEWATER BEACH, ELSEY, FORSYTH,
GLADDEN, GOODHOPE, GRAFF, GREER, HOLLISTER, HOWES, HUGGINS,
INDIAN POINT, JADWIN, KIMBERLING CITY, KIRBYVILLE, LAKE SPRING,
MANSFIELD, MARSHFIELD, MONTIER, MOUNTAIN GROVE, NIXA, NORTHVIEW,
OZARK, OZARK BEACH, PLATO, POMONA, POTTERSVILLE, POWERSITE, ROBY,
ROGERSVILLE, ROME, SALEM, SELMORE, SEYMOUR, SILOAM SPRINGS,
SILVER DOLLAR CITY, SOUTH FORK, SPRINGFIELD, SQUIRES, TERESITA,
THAYER, THOMASVILLE, VANZANT, WASOLA, WEST PLAINS, WHITE CHURCK,
WILDERNESS, AND WINONA.
